75
00:06:22,670 --> 00:06:23,910
But actually...

76
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,410
I'm helpless with many things.

77
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,350
As Mr. Qichao said,

78
00:06:35,730 --> 00:06:38,390
"The flames of passion can't be extinguished."

79
00:06:40,550 --> 00:06:42,010
Let's take it step by step.

80
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,860
Even Sun Yat-sen had to compromise a lot

81
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:46,570
at the start of his revolution,

82
00:06:46,570 --> 00:06:47,640
let alone us.

83
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:49,760
I can compromise and tolerate.

84
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:51,840
But I don't want

85
00:06:52,909 --> 00:06:54,260
to become like Lin Qiaosong

86
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:55,280
where it's a habit.

87
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,880
You won't.

88
00:06:56,290 --> 00:06:57,250
You're different.

89
00:06:57,250 --> 00:06:58,680
He was once passionate

90
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,830
with ambitions and ideals...

91
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:00,950
I said, you won't!

92
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:18,990
Trust me.

93
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:20,820
Let's move on

94
00:07:20,820 --> 00:07:21,990
and look forward,

95
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:22,860
