96
00:07:24,890 --> 00:07:25,920
As long as we don't give up,

97
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,440
we can change everything.

98
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:29,040
We...

99
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:31,390
We have to carry this burden

100
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:32,750
so that the ones we love,

101
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:34,220
the next generation,

102
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,490
and the next

103
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:39,170
can truly have

104
00:07:39,490 --> 00:07:40,300
better lives.

105
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:44,890
Look at me.

106
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:48,370
Trust me.

107
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:52,750
Don't forget your roots.

108
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:53,920
I won't.

109
00:07:54,659 --> 00:07:56,520
Now repeat your original belief.

110
00:07:56,630 --> 00:07:57,280
Serve the country.

111
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,080
Again.

112
00:07:58,190 --> 00:07:59,250
Serve the country!

113
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,360
Serve the country!

114
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,350
Embed this in your bones

115
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:03,610
and your blood.

116
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,830
If you let me down,

117
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,480
I'll kick you out myself.

118
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,000
Yes.

119
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,600
Remember.

120
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,240
Yes.

121
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,310
From now on,

122
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:22,760
Wei Ruolai

123
00:08:23,570 --> 00:08:25,120
will be my last apprentice.

124
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,880
I'm his teacher

125
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:28,480
and political guarantor.

126
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,480
I'll remember it.

127
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,610
I'll try my best

128
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,250
and not let you down.

129
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,240
Okay.

130
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:12,720
Thank you.

