183
00:15:48,430 --> 00:15:49,240
Maybe...

184
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,670
Don't wait for me.

185
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,400
Marry a dependable man.

186
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,000
Don't go for those

187
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:05,720
who use guns.

188
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:09,150
Pointless.

189
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:14,840
