194
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:26,550
I...

195
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,150
I was joking.

196
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:29,890
I'm Lin Qiaosong's wife.

197
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:32,000
You promised me!

198
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:36,030
There are only two things in my life.

199
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:37,000
First,

200
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:38,940
to find my brother.

201
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:40,910
Second,

202
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,200
to marry you.

203
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,600
It's just a few years.

204
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:54,910
I'll wait.

205
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:58,120
We'll be good when you get out.

206
00:17:14,390 --> 00:17:15,910
You're such a fool.

207
