Get off.

217
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:03,410
Get off!

218
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:04,880
Hurry!

219
00:19:23,360 --> 00:19:25,670
I heard someone paid a lot to bail us out.

220
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:27,080
It's you?

221
00:19:27,430 --> 00:19:28,360
Sorry, Hao.

222
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:31,060
Our brothers lost their lives

223
00:19:31,470 --> 00:19:32,600
and status.

224
00:19:35,820 --> 00:19:37,880
As long as we're alive, there's hope.

225
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:40,960
It's lucky that a few of us

226
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,130
are still alive.

227
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,040
It's not your fault.

228
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:46,300
Blame feudalism poisoning minds.

229
00:19:47,490 --> 00:19:49,380
I finally understand why

230
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:50,910
people in your hometown

231
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,040
risked it all

232
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,780
to join the Red Army.

233
00:20:13,130 --> 00:20:13,990
Here,

234
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,250
I promise

235
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:18,320
the Investigation and Arrest Unit is clean.

236
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:20,480
The police work hard

237
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:22,050
to protect the citizens.

238
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,760
Except for Captain Lin,

239
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:26,310
the rest are criminals who made counterfeit coins.

240
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:27,230
Kill them all!

241
00:20:27,230 --> 00:20:29,990
As carters, they distributed counterfeit coins

242
00:20:29,990 --> 00:20:31,710
everywhere.

243
00:20:46,530 --> 00:20:47,350
Miss Shen?

244
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:49,570
You're back.

245
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:51,430
Why are you here?

246
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,440
When did you come?

247
00:20:52,990 --> 00:20:53,670
Just now.

248
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:55,180
Have a bowl too.

249
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:57,710
Okay.

250
00:20:59,150 --> 00:20:59,800
Boss,

251
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:01,620
another bowl of wontons.

252
00:21:07,900 --> 00:21:08,540
Why?

253
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:10,150
Do you still feel bad?

254
00:21:12,910 --> 00:21:13,630
It's okay.

255
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:15,240
It'll only get worse.

256
00:21:15,390 --> 00:21:16,450
Just get used to it.

257
00:21:24,230 --> 00:21:24,990
What is this?

258
00:21:26,080 --> 00:21:26,940
A medical book.

259
00:21:27,370 --> 00:21:28,230
A medical book?

260
00:21:29,080 --> 00:21:29,880
I think

261
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:32,360
you're in urgent need of it.

262
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:41,790
[The Capital]

263
00:21:47,230 --> 00:21:50,350
You're feeling pain and frustrated

264
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:52,900
because our country has gotten sick.

265
00:21:53,430 --> 00:21:54,990
This book is the cure.

266
00:21:56,110 --> 00:21:57,770
Whenever I meet a difficulty,

267
00:21:58,360 --> 00:22:00,760
and feel a bit disappointed with what I'm dealing with,

268
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:02,220
I would open it and read it.

269
00:22:04,150 --> 00:22:05,280
You can give it a try.

270
00:22:05,770 --> 00:22:07,570
Ask me if you have any questions.

271
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:16,590
But don't tell my brother about it.

272
00:22:30,990 --> 00:22:32,450
Why are you folding these?

273
00:22:35,370 --> 00:22:37,930
So many people died in the mint that produced counterfeit coins.

274
00:22:37,930 --> 00:22:40,130
We should at least do something, right?

275
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,990
Though we can't give them real money,

276
00:22:41,990 --> 00:22:43,990
we should make a gesture of good will

277
00:22:44,080 --> 00:22:45,410
by offering joss paper.

278
00:23:06,290 --> 00:23:09,090
Any progress in your relationship with Miss Shen?

279
00:23:09,280 --> 00:23:10,840
We're not in a relationship.

280
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:11,970
We're just friends.

281
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,670
Aren't you gonna marry her?

282
00:23:13,670 --> 00:23:15,360
She's just a friend. Didn't I just tell you?

283
00:23:15,360 --> 00:23:16,560
Why would I marry her?

284
00:23:18,120 --> 00:23:19,050
In that case,

285
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:21,340
