286
00:23:22,470 --> 00:23:23,320
Are you leaving for home?

287
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:24,920
We're both leaving for home.

288
00:23:26,470 --> 00:23:28,020
Your father misses you so much.

289
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,300
He always talks about you.

290
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:31,360
I've gotten an earful of his nagging.

291
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:33,160
You can go back if you want to.

292
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:34,280
