440
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:35,610
I thought I owed him my life,

441
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:38,990
and was indebted to his family.

442
00:31:44,530 --> 00:31:45,480
Later on,

443
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,840
I gradually understood

444
00:31:51,470 --> 00:31:52,760
that all of us

445
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:54,760
shared the same name.

446
00:31:55,910 --> 00:31:57,080
