449
00:32:04,900 --> 00:32:06,510
We have common aspirations.

450
00:32:07,630 --> 00:32:09,040
To reach our goals,

451
00:32:09,730 --> 00:32:11,160
we'd make joint efforts,

452
00:32:12,460 --> 00:32:13,920
stand in solidarity,

453
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:16,120
and put absolute trust in each other.

454
00:32:20,990 --> 00:32:21,950
Since then,

455
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,860
every time I work on a mission,

456
00:32:26,250 --> 00:32:28,510
I would always prepare myself for death.

457
00:32:28,540 --> 00:32:29,850
I've near feared it,

