00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:38,200
I wouldn't be a lonely soul,

461
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,080
as I'm backed

462
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:42,740
by tens of thousands of comrades.

463
00:32:44,670 --> 00:32:46,950
They'll walk steadfastly toward

464
00:32:47,910 --> 00:32:49,440
towards our shared vision.

